{"version":1,"entries":{"person_2112859_translations":{"at":1773384111856,"data":{"id":2112859,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Han So-hee (born Lee So-hee on November 18, 1993) is a South Korean actress. She began her career as a supporting character in the television series Money Flower (2017), 100 Days My Prince (2018), and Abyss (2019) before transitioning into lead roles in The World of the Married (2020), Nevertheless (2021), and My Name (2021).","name":"Han So-hee","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"한소희","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"本名\t이 소 희（Lee Sohee）李韶禧\n\n原文名\t한소희  音译名 韩韶禧  大陆常译为 韩素希\n\n罗马拼音\tHan Sohee\n\n国籍\t 南韩\n\n出生\t1994年11月18日（26岁）南韩蔚山广域市  职业\t演员、模特儿\n\n语言\t韩语\n\n教育程度\t蔚山艺术高等学校\n\n出道日期\t2016年11月15日\n\n出道作品\t《Tell Me What To Do》\n\n代表作品  《金钱之花》《百日的郎君》《夫妇的世界》《无法抗拒的他》《以吾之名》\n\n活跃年代\t2016年－至今\n\n经纪公司\t9ato Entertainment","name":"韩韶禧","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"Han So Hee je jihokorejská herečka. Han So So debutovala menší rolí ve \"Reunited Worlds\". V roce 2017 se objevila ve videoklipu Jung Yong Hwa \"That Girl\" a v roce 2016 ve videoklipu skupiny SHINee \"Tell Me What To Do\". V roce 2018 získala své první hlavní role v seriálech \"Money Flower\" televize MBC a \"100 Days My Prince\" televize tvN. Zahrála si také v seriálu KBS2 \"After The Rain\". Objevila se také ve snímku Roye Kima \"The Hardest Part\". V roce 2019 si Han zahrála vedlejší roli v seriálu \"Hlubina\" po boku hlavních představitelů Ahn Hyo Seop a Park Bo Young. V roce 2021 si zahrála hlavní role v seriálech Nicméně a Modrá až na kost.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韓韶禧（韓語：한소희，英語：Han So-Hee；1994年11月18日—），本名李韶禧（韓語：이소희，英語：Lee So-Hee），韓國女演員、模特兒，常譯名為韓素希。代表作品《金錢之花》《夫婦的世界》《無法抗拒的他》《以吾之名》《單戀原聲帶》","name":"韓韶禧","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ฮันโซฮี","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"Η Λι Σο-χι (Lee So-hee), περισσότερο γνωστή με το καλλιτεχνικό όνομα Χαν Σο-χι (Han So-hee), είναι μια Νοτιοκορεάτισσα ηθοποιός. Ξεκίνησε την καριέρα της ως δευτερεύων χαρακτήρας στις τηλεοπτικές σειρές Money Flower (2017), 100 Days My Prince (2018) και Abyss (2019) πριν μεταβεί σε πρωταγωνιστικούς ρόλους στο The World of the Married (2020), Nevertheless (2021) , My Name (2021) και Gyeongseong Creature (2023–2024).","name":"Χαν Σο-χι","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"Хан Со Хи (родилась Ли Со Хи 18 ноября 1993 года) - южнокорейская актриса. Начала свою карьеру в качестве персонажа второго плана в телесериалах \"Денежный цветок\" (2017), \"Мой принц на 100 дней\" (2018) и \"Бездна\" (2019), а затем получила главные роли в фильмах \"Мир женатой пары\" (2020), \"Тем не менее\" (2021) и \"Моё имя\" (2021).","name":"Хан Со Хи","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Han So-hee (née Lee So-hee le 18 novembre 1993) est une actrice sud-coréenne. Elle a commencé sa carrière en tant que personnage secondaire dans les séries télévisées Money Flower (2017), 100 Days My Prince (2018) et Abyss (2019) avant de passer aux rôles principaux dans The World of the Married (2020), Nevertheless (2021) et My Name (2021).","name":"Han So-hee","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韓韶禧（韓語：한소희，英語：Han So - Hee；1994 年 11 月 18 日—），本名李韶禧（韓語：이소희，英語：Lee So - Hee），韓國女演員、模特兒，常譯名為韓素希。代表作品《金錢之花》《夫婦的世界》《無法抗拒的他》《以吾之名》《單戀原聲帶》","name":"韓韶禧","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Han So-hee","primary":false}}]}},"person_1180738_translations":{"at":1772865009455,"data":{"id":1180738,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Johann Nikolussi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CH","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Johann Nikolussi","primary":true}}]}},"movie_1554565_credits":{"at":1773039162585,"data":{"id":1554565,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":53252,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Noel Gugliemi","original_name":"Noel Gugliemi","popularity":1.6319,"profile_path":"/8jujXofjpSroMQ1R2JLB0GWIPor.jpg","cast_id":1,"character":"Father Hector","credit_id":"68db179b32fe147ee7e1cf4d","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":3032871,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"April Clark","original_name":"April Clark","popularity":0.2559,"profile_path":"/tAlQaIwfRmb3GZ3DnnFY1s23YYW.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"Maria","credit_id":"68db17a7646a7ecc3cb41dd9","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2228027,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Evan James Henderson","original_name":"Evan James Henderson","popularity":0.1711,"profile_path":"/ae4oXMgloywUnQWubAnbgMEiwft.jpg","cast_id":3,"character":"Zack","credit_id":"68db17c43f49357a46b9a54d","order":2},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":4904096,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Neeley Dayan",